library(Seurat)
library(magrittr)
my.samples <- list()

my.samples[[1]] <- readRDS("~/spinal_cord_paper/data/Gg_lumb_1_seurat_060223.rds")
my.samples[[2]] <- readRDS("~/spinal_cord_paper/data/Gg_lumb_2_seurat_060223.rds")

names(my.samples) <- c("Gg_lumb_1", "Gg_lumb_2")
# integration features
features <- SelectIntegrationFeatures(
    object.list = my.samples,
    nfeatures = 3000
    )

# prepare integration 
my.samples <- PrepSCTIntegration(
    object.list = my.samples,
    anchor.features = features
    )

# find anchors
NT.anchors <- FindIntegrationAnchors(
    object.list = my.samples,
    normalization.method = "SCT",
    anchor.features = features
    )

rm(my.samples)

# integrate
int.nt.sct <- IntegrateData(
    anchorset = NT.anchors,
    # features.to.integrate = all_features,
    normalization.method = "SCT"
    )

# compute PCA
int.nt.sct <- RunPCA(
    int.nt.sct,
    verbose = FALSE
    )

# Run UMAP
int.nt.sct <- RunUMAP(
    int.nt.sct,
    reduction = "pca",
    dims = 1:30
    )
